channel.title: Help adding a teleport
channel.description:
I've been looking in ClickingMost.java and I found nothing to create a new teleport.
But I found where to write the name on it. It was blank before:
[IMG]http://i380.photobucket.com/albums/oo245/zamorak_album_2008/duel.jpg[/img]
Could you help me and find the place where to create the teleport with Coords please ?
Thanks.

item.title: Help adding a teleport
item.dc:creator: @CoonHunter CoonHunter
item.description:
@CoonHunter wrote:

[quote=“d man103456, post:5, topic:293097”]The only thing is his base is most likely delta so he has the

+misc.random(#)

So its not that simple, he is going to have to try and find through searching in clickmost.java. Simply teleporting there won’t help him.[/quote]
FOr your information, with the + misc.random() thing, its still posible to find it, you simple teleport a few times and figure out if its random or not. That solves that problem. If it is, find its barrier corrdinates that it doesnt teleport past.
